{"ocr_results":[{"text":"(6)","box":[[757,100],[804,100],[804,128],[757,128]]},{"text":"as before, perhaps only a bit less strict with regard to class background","box":[[168,185],[1362,184],[1362,212],[168,213]]},{"text":"and historical background.I don't think there is much use in joining","box":[[168,215],[1314,218],[1314,248],[167,244]]},{"text":"the youth league。","box":[[170,252],[480,252],[480,276],[170,276]]},{"text":"The benefits are not all that clear。","box":[[476,248],[1083,252],[1082,278],[475,275]]},{"text":"The main one","box":[[1098,252],[1295,252],[1295,276],[1098,276]]},{"text":"is that you can become a party member，and this is important for promotion","box":[[167,284],[1377,284],[1377,311],[167,311]]},{"text":"later on. To be the head of the shop or department you must be a party","box":[[166,315],[1329,317],[1329,347],[165,345]]},{"text":"member.(","box":[[167,351],[321,351],[321,375],[167,375]]},{"text":"Other thanthat there are nospecialadvantages。","box":[[311,349],[1100,352],[1099,379],[311,376]]},{"text":"Relations between masses and activists:I heard that relations were","box":[[249,381],[1361,383],[1361,410],[249,407]]},{"text":"all right in the l950s， because the league and the party did a good job.","box":[[167,416],[1343,416],[1343,443],[167,443]]},{"text":"But the quality of the membership went down after that.1","box":[[167,450],[1104,450],[1104,474],[167,474]]},{"text":"Now it doesn't","box":[[1094,450],[1328,447],[1328,471],[1095,474]]},{"text":"sound good to say you are in the youth league. Many people now call it","box":[[164,480],[1331,479],[1331,512],[164,513]]},{"text":"the laji tuan (garbage league).","box":[[168,515],[680,515],[680,542],[168,542]]},{"text":"There is some abuse of the young members","box":[[704,514],[1360,515],[1360,542],[704,541]]},{"text":"by the young workers， just like in school，but not a lot。","box":[[167,549],[1119,549],[1119,575],[167,575]]},{"text":"An example:","box":[[1130,549],[1311,549],[1311,573],[1130,573]]},{"text":"Sometimes they ask for blood donations。","box":[[165,580],[810,579],[810,606],[165,607]]},{"text":"Chinese hate doing this，because","box":[[838,580],[1363,580],[1363,607],[838,607]]},{"text":"they think it takes away your soul.","box":[[167,612],[769,612],[769,645],[167,645]]},{"text":"The workers willturntothe league","box":[[772,612],[1346,614],[1346,641],[771,639]]},{"text":"members and say, \"You give blood, you're","box":[[161,643],[830,639],[830,676],[162,680]]},{"text":"the league member!\"","box":[[832,646],[1152,641],[1152,672],[833,677]]},{"text":"Activists and youth leaguers are not exactly","box":[[251,678],[975,680],[975,707],[251,705]]},{"text":"thesamethingbecause","box":[[962,681],[1345,681],[1345,704],[962,704]]},{"text":"there are some activists who are too old for the youth league。","box":[[169,711],[1188,713],[1188,740],[169,737]]},{"text":"There are","box":[[1215,713],[1361,715],[1360,739],[1215,736]]},{"text":"two kinds of activists:","box":[[170,746],[550,745],[550,769],[170,770]]},{"text":"the political activists and backbones during","box":[[577,742],[1298,744],[1298,774],[577,772]]},{"text":"campaigns, and those who are activists in production。","box":[[171,778],[1043,777],[1043,804],[171,805]]},{"text":"The first kind are","box":[[1066,777],[1360,778],[1360,802],[1066,801]]},{"text":"not really","box":[[170,812],[336,812],[336,836],[170,836]]},{"text":"considered genuine activists by the masses，","box":[[330,810],[1072,812],[1072,839],[330,837]]},{"text":"they are actually","box":[[1066,812],[1343,812],[1343,839],[1066,839]]},{"text":"despised (mieshi)。","box":[[171,843],[467,842],[468,867],[172,868]]},{"text":"But the second kind are considered real","box":[[493,843],[1141,844],[1141,868],[493,867]]},{"text":" activists ,","box":[[1128,841],[1329,846],[1328,873],[1127,867]]},{"text":"they don't rely on their mouth to eat。 In recent years the second kind","box":[[170,875],[1331,875],[1331,904],[170,904]]},{"text":"of activist is more common。","box":[[170,907],[610,912],[610,935],[169,931]]},{"text":"ShopOrganization","box":[[168,975],[449,973],[450,1001],[169,1003]]},{"text":"Attendance checking--leaves, both medical and personal, the times","box":[[251,1008],[1312,1006],[1312,1033],[251,1035]]},{"text":"people come in and leave.1","box":[[168,1042],[617,1038],[617,1065],[169,1070]]},{"text":"No time clocks。 Handled by the small groups。","box":[[606,1039],[1345,1041],[1345,1068],[606,1065]]},{"text":"But time checking","box":[[168,1070],[453,1074],[452,1100],[167,1097]]},{"text":"is not too tight,its easy to come late and leave early.","box":[[460,1073],[1375,1073],[1375,1100],[460,1100]]},{"text":"People also leave in the middle of the day。","box":[[166,1103],[907,1104],[907,1134],[166,1133]]},{"text":"The group leader knows this,","box":[[903,1106],[1361,1106],[1361,1133],[903,1133]]},{"text":"but covers it up and doesn't report it。","box":[[167,1139],[827,1139],[827,1166],[167,1166]]},{"text":"Why?E","box":[[836,1140],[947,1140],[947,1164],[836,1164]]},{"text":"Because he does not want","box":[[935,1140],[1329,1140],[1329,1164],[935,1164]]},{"text":"bad relations in the group， doesn't want other workers to oppose him in","box":[[169,1172],[1330,1172],[1330,1199],[169,1199]]},{"text":"assessments for raises, and doesn't want","box":[[168,1206],[831,1203],[831,1229],[169,1233]]},{"text":"them to oppose him。","box":[[817,1206],[1158,1206],[1158,1232],[817,1232]]},{"text":"Thiswould","box":[[1185,1206],[1345,1206],[1345,1227],[1185,1227]]},{"text":"just make things difficult in the shop。","box":[[169,1235],[844,1235],[844,1265],[169,1265]]},{"text":"If the problem is so serious that","box":[[839,1238],[1378,1238],[1378,1262],[839,1262]]},{"text":"it affects production, then the group","box":[[170,1272],[782,1272],[782,1296],[170,1296]]},{"text":"） leader will report it， but most","box":[[770,1270],[1297,1271],[1297,1295],[770,1294]]},{"text":"likely he first of all will tell the worker involved and warn him first.","box":[[172,1302],[1345,1302],[1345,1329],[172,1329]]},{"text":"But because group leaders are also workers,","box":[[166,1336],[880,1334],[880,1365],[167,1367]]},{"text":"they would rather not enforce","box":[[886,1335],[1361,1337],[1361,1364],[886,1362]]},{"text":"rules so strictly that conflicts arise.。","box":[[169,1369],[811,1368],[811,1394],[169,1396]]},{"text":"As","box":[[828,1371],[877,1371],[877,1393],[828,1393]]},{"text":"61ong","box":[[866,1371],[958,1371],[958,1394],[866,1394]]},{"text":"gastheycancontinue","box":[[946,1370],[1301,1370],[1301,1393],[946,1393]]},{"text":"eto","box":[[1291,1374],[1344,1374],[1344,1392],[1291,1392]]},{"text":"get by, they will let it slide.","box":[[168,1405],[677,1399],[677,1427],[169,1432]]},{"text":"For a period at the end of the CR they said that systems of rules and","box":[[249,1435],[1381,1431],[1381,1459],[249,1463]]},{"text":"regulations fettered worker activism.","box":[[171,1470],[812,1466],[812,1493],[172,1497]]},{"text":"Since 1977 or 78 they have revived","box":[[807,1468],[1363,1468],[1363,1492],[807,1492]]},{"text":"them。","box":[[171,1503],[289,1505],[289,1529],[170,1527]]},{"text":"The job responsibility system (gangwei zeren zhi).T","box":[[278,1501],[1144,1497],[1144,1527],[278,1531]]},{"text":"This is the system","box":[[1131,1500],[1430,1504],[1429,1528],[1130,1524]]},{"text":"thatwasrestored。","box":[[171,1538],[500,1538],[500,1560],[171,1560]]},{"text":"The systemsof jobresponsibilityarespecifiedfor","box":[[495,1535],[1331,1534],[1331,1560],[495,1561]]},{"text":"each job on the floor.","box":[[168,1568],[531,1567],[531,1594],[169,1595]]},{"text":"They have restored its name and put up","box":[[561,1567],[1190,1567],[1190,1594],[561,1594]]},{"text":"）lists，but","box":[[1177,1569],[1360,1569],[1360,1593],[1177,1593]]},{"text":"no one really checks on its implementation.","box":[[165,1602],[891,1598],[891,1626],[166,1630]]},{"text":"It has some effect, but not","box":[[903,1600],[1347,1602],[1347,1626],[903,1624]]},{"text":"avery","box":[[167,1639],[271,1637],[271,1659],[168,1661]]},{"text":"large one。","box":[[263,1636],[488,1637],[488,1661],[263,1660]]},{"text":"It does helpon a daily basis to tell who is responsible","box":[[475,1633],[1395,1633],[1395,1660],[475,1660]]},{"text":"for a mistake onithe floor,it also tells people how they are to handle their","box":[[168,1667],[1427,1667],[1427,1694],[168,1694]]},{"text":"job。","box":[[170,1703],[265,1703],[265,1727],[170,1727]]},{"text":"They did not have any concrete activity like study groups to implement","box":[[264,1699],[1413,1699],[1413,1728],[264,1728]]},{"text":"these regulations.","box":[[167,1734],[472,1732],[473,1759],[168,1761]]},{"text":"They posted them on a board and that was about it.","box":[[494,1731],[1318,1730],[1318,1760],[494,1761]]},{"text":"They","box":[[1348,1733],[1412,1738],[1410,1762],[1346,1757]]},{"text":"diditbecausetheabove","box":[[169,1768],[562,1768],[562,1791],[169,1791]]},{"text":"levels said that they had to spell","box":[[578,1767],[1141,1767],[1141,1791],[578,1791]]},{"text":"outthesystem","box":[[1129,1766],[1382,1769],[1381,1792],[1128,1789]]},{"text":"of job responsibilities.","box":[[166,1801],[566,1798],[566,1826],[167,1829]]},{"text":"But they didn't","box":[[596,1800],[842,1800],[842,1824],[596,1824]]},{"text":"give much thought to it otherwise.","box":[[835,1796],[1412,1798],[1411,1828],[835,1826]]},{"text":"Reports (baobiao):","box":[[249,1834],[550,1831],[550,1858],[249,1861]]},{"text":"production reports every day, go to the production","box":[[575,1832],[1399,1832],[1399,1862],[575,1862]]},{"text":"department, and every month they had a report on the progress in meeting","box":[[169,1864],[1350,1864],[1350,1896],[169,1896]]},{"text":"the eight big targets, and also attendance and labor reports.","box":[[167,1898],[1204,1897],[1204,1927],[167,1928]]},{"text":"They were all","box":[[1198,1899],[1413,1899],[1413,1926],[1198,19